data.description: Welcome to your new home overlooking the rapidly growing town of Chehalis! This is a great opportunity to live in the heart of town & be in near proximity to so many convenient places. Home is rather spacious, w/3bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, open living room w/wood fireplace, dining room & good sized kitchen. It also has 600+ square feet of basement that includes the garage, utility room, & water heater. Home is located on a corner lot w/good sized yard, & only a short walk to Safeway, Ace Hardware, & Penny Playground. Less than 2-3 minute drive to I-5, & centrally located between Seattle & Portland. Come make this YOUR home, today!
